headline: FIS to Present at Upcoming Conference
summary: JACKSONVILLE, Fla., November 25, 2024--FIS® (NYSE: FIS), a global leader in financial technology, will present on Wednesday, Dec. 4, 2024, at the UBS Global Technology and AI Conference at 11:35 a.m. (MST).
